c: 25
v: 3
t: "Yallak kalah yallittey tu-gine wayta haysiten usun sinnih ginniime marah anuk, kaadu sinni nafsik umaané waasaanam maduudaanaay, tuxxiq kaah orbisaanam maduudan, kaadu nuwwam qidaanam maduudaanaay, Rabtem yaynuwweenim maduudan, kaadu rabtem magooqak nuwwuk ugsaanaah kobxisaanam maduudan"